records.name: Aina Residency Beachfront Hotel

descriptions.hotel: Make yourself at home in one of the 11 guestrooms, featuring kitchens with full-sized refrigerators/freezers and ovens. Rooms have private balconies or patios. Complimentary wireless internet access keeps you connected, and 40-inch Smart televisions are provided for your entertainment. Conveniences include safes and separate sitting areas, and housekeeping is provided daily.
descriptions.direction: With a stay at Aina Residency Beachfront Hotel, you'll be centrally located in Hulhumalé, within a 15-minute drive of Maldives Islamic Centre and Hulhumalé Central Park. This beach aparthotel is 0.5 mi (0.8 km) from Hulhumale Beach and 3 mi (4.9 km) from Victory Wreck Dive Site.
descriptions.other: A roundtrip airport shuttle is complimentary (available 24 hours).
